# Experiment: Spec-Driven UI

## Context

The Food Logging UI was generated using a design contract and AI prompt.

## What worked

- Clear design contract helped AI generate correct layout
- UI matched expected structure
- Easy to connect UI with existing reducer logic

## Issues

- AI sometimes ignored spacing rules
- Needed manual corrections

## Result

Spec-driven UI approach improves consistency and speeds up development, but still requires manual validation.